┌────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  VPC: 10.0.0.0/16                     │
│                                        │
│  Public Subnets (3 AZs):              │
│  → Load Balancers                     │
│  → NAT Gateways                       │
│  → Bastion Host                       │
│                                        │
│  Private Subnets (3 AZs):             │
│  → EKS Worker Nodes                   │
