│  → ElastiCache                        │
│                                        │
│  Isolated Subnets (3 AZs):            │
│  → RDS Primary                        │
│  → Backup Storage                     │
└────────────────────────────────────────┘

Compute:
  Orchestration:   AWS EKS (Kubernetes)
  Node Groups:
    → General: t3.xlarge (4 vCPU, 16GB)
    → AI:      g4dn.xlarge (GPU)
    → Memory:  r6i.large (memory optimized)

  Auto Scaling:
    Min: 2 nodes per group
    Max: 20 nodes per group
    Metric: CPU > 70% OR Memory > 80%

Load Balancing:
  External: AWS ALB (Application LB)
  Internal: AWS NLB (Network LB)
  Algorithm: Least Outstanding Requests

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
Kubernetes Architecture
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Namespaces:
  production:   Services في الـ Production
  staging:      Services في الـ Staging
  monitoring:   Prometheus + Grafana
  ingress:      Nginx Ingress Controller

Per Service (Deployment):
  Replicas:     min 2, max 10
  Strategy:     RollingUpdate
  Resources:
    requests: cpu: 250m, memory: 512Mi
    limits:   cpu: 1000m, memory: 2Gi

  Health Checks:
    Liveness:   GET /health (30s interval)
    Readiness:  GET /ready (10s interval)

  Pod Disruption Budget:
    minAvailable: 1 (ensures no downtime)

HPA (Horizontal Pod Autoscaler):
  Metric:       CPU Utilization > 70%
  Scale Up:     +2 pods (stabilization: 60s)
  Scale Down:   -1 pod (stabilization: 300s)
```

