     → Soft delete immediately
     → Hard delete after 30 days
     → Some data retained for legal reasons:
       (Financial transactions, Audit logs)

  ✅ Right to Data Portability:
     → JSON + CSV export available
     → Standard formats

  ✅ Right to Object:
     → Opt-out of AI processing
     → Opt-out of marketing
     → Opt-out of analytics

Data Localization:
  → Saudi users' data: me-central-1 (UAE)
    or me-south-1 (Bahrain)
  → No transfer outside GCC without consent
  → Data Processing Agreements with all vendors

